<div class="contyishang">
<div style="height:30px; font-weight:bold; font-size:16px; margin-bottom:10px; clear:both;">
<h2><span style="float:left;">创作背景</span></h2>
<a style="float:left; margin-top:7px; margin-left:5px;" href="javascript:PlayShangxi(36674)"><img id="speakerimgShangxi36674" src="/img/speaker.png" / alt="" width="16" height="16"/></a>
<span id="shangxiPlay36674" style=" display:none;width:1px; height:1px; float:left;"></span>
</div>
　　关于此<a href="https://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv_10c5983a856c.aspx">诗</a>的主旨与背景，历来有多种观点。《毛诗序》云：“《十亩之间》，刺时也。言其国削小，民无所居焉。”另外还有人主张“情诗恋歌”说，即把“行与子还”、“行与子逝”，解释为姑娘招呼自己的情侣一同走。而今人多解此诗为描写采桑女偕伴而归时的诗歌。
</div>
<div class="dingpai">
<a id="dingsx36674" href="javascript:dingsx('36674','http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=10c5983a856c')">有用(0)</a><a id="paisx36674" style=" margin-left:10px;" href="javascript:paisx('36674','http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=10c5983a856c')">没用(0)</a>
</div>
